examples.en: He riffled through the papers on his desk.
examples.ru: Он пролистал лежащие на столе бумаги.

examples.en: He riffled the pages of the magazine.
The magician riffled through the cards with skilful fingers.
It only took him a few moments riffling through the records to find the right name.
examples.ru: Всего за несколько мгновений он пролистал свои записи и нашёл нужное имя.
